## Development Guidelines

- Use Korean comments and documentation for business logic
- Follow Spring Boot best practices for backend
- Use TypeScript for all frontend components
- Implement proper error handling and validation
- Use JWT for authentication
- Follow RESTful API design principles
- Use React Query for data fetching and caching
- Follow Yarn Workspaces for package management
- Use named exports for all components (no default exports)
- Implement proper memoization for performance optimization
